            <note xml:id="foot.f3">Lewes refers to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2749.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Alexander Onufrievich Kovalevsky</ref> and to A. O. Kovalevsky 1866. See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 15, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-5443.xml" resp="#automat">letter from V. O. Kovalevsky, 15 March 1867</ref> and n. 6.</note>
